131Ch 16:8 Give thanks to the LORD and proclaim his greatness.Let the whole world know what he has done.
131Ch 16:9 Sing to him; yes, sing his praises.Tell everyone about his wonderful deeds.
131Ch 16:10 Exult in his holy name; rejoice, you who worship the LORD.
