131Ch 16:25 Great is the LORD! He is most worthy of praise! He is to be feared above all gods.
131Ch 16:26 The gods of other nations are mere idols, but the LORD made the heavens!
131Ch 16:27 Honor and majesty surround him; strength and joy fill his dwelling.
131Ch 16:28 O nations of the world, recognize the LORD, recognize that the LORD is glorious and strong.
131Ch 16:29 Give to the LORD the glory he deserves! Bring your offering and come into his presence. Worship the LORD in all his holy splendor.
131Ch 16:30 Let all the earth tremble before him.The world stands firm and cannot be shaken.
