131Ch 23:14 As for Moses, the man of God, his sons were included with the tribe of Levi.
131Ch 23:15 The sons of Moses were Gershom and Eliezer.
131Ch 23:16 The descendants of Gershom included Shebuel, the family leader.
131Ch 23:17 Eliezer had only one son, Rehabiah, the family leader. Rehabiah had numerous descendants.
131Ch 23:18 The descendants of Izhar included Shelomith, the family leader.
131Ch 23:19 The descendants of Hebron included Jeriah (the family leader), Amariah (the second), Jahaziel (the third), and Jekameam (the fourth).
